author: lan3v0
body:
I'm using a Canadian brokerage account (on PC) and was pressing F5 every 5 seconds to refresh the option page. I did this maybe 2-3 minutes when i finally decided to bid .10 cents higher at that particular time but even after waiting 1-2 minutes, it never got filled in. I was also suspecting that maybe that it was on the brokerage side but I was simultaneously checking the SPY option prices on Barchart and they were the same.
It never really happened to me before. I usually put mid price on other options ticker with high liquidity and they usually get filled in almost instantly.
